headline: Lennox is the First HVAC OEM to Complete the U.S. Department of Energy's Commercial Building HVAC Technology Challenge Lab Validation
summary: Lennox (NYSE: LII), a leader in energy-efficient climate solutions, announced that its commercial cold climate heat pump rooftop unit (RTU) was the first to successfully complete the laboratory validation for commercial unitary equipment in the 15-25 tons category in the U.S. Department of Energy's (DOE) Commercial Building HVAC Technology Challenge.

headline: Lennox International announces layoffs at Marshalltown plant
summary: Lennox International cites business needs and current conditions as it announces layoffs at its plant in Marshalltown, where the company was founded
